short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds a section with a ChatGPT reply to the search results

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ChatGPT Search Assistant is an innovative Chrome extension that enhances your online search experience by integrating the power of artificial intelligence into your Google search results. With this extension, you'll receive comprehensive, AI-generated responses from ChatGPT alongside your standard search outcomes. This not only provides deeper insights and more detailed information on your queries but also saves you time by consolidating multiple sources into succinct, intelligible responses. Ideal for researchers, students, and anyone looking to supercharge their browsing efficiency, ChatGPT Search Assistant makes information gathering more intuitive and effective than ever.
